# install homebrew
```$ /usr/bin/ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)"```

# install mysql
```brew info mysql```
```brew install mysql```

# install brew services
```brew tap homebrew/services```

# start mysql service
```brew services start mysql```
```brew services list```
```mysql -V```

# mysql manage
```mysqladmin -u root password 'passwordhere'```
